            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ Diem mercurii qui est septimo kalendas aprelis, presentia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum nomina subter
                        leguntur, in <placeName
                            key="#Villas #Mills #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals"
                            ref="#places/399"><rs key="#Villas">villa</rs> Asspi</placeName>
                        pertinentia <rs key="#Castle">castris</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/145">Nogarie</placeName> per vuasonem
                        terre que in sua tenebat manu, <persName
                            key="#Mills #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Rosa/f. Dominici">Rosa</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs> quondam <persName key="faherOf"><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName> investivit <persName
                            key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Dominicus/monachus"
                            >Dominicum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiterum</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Mills #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Priests #Monks"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName> positum inter
                            <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4196">Padum</placeName> et
                            <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4197">Largionem</placeName> ad
                        iura ipsius monasterii de omnibus rebus territoriis iuris sui seu et de
                        parte <rs key="#Mills">molendini</rs> quem habere in <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4410">Tartaro</placeName>, tam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sediminis</rs> quam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> cum <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Cereals">arabilis</rs>, tam in eadem villa Asspi quam in
                        pertinentiis predicti castri seu in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/124"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/59"
                            >Veronese</placeName></geogName>, ita ut faciat exinde a presenti die
                        pars ipsius monasterii aut cuius pars monasterii dederit <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario nomine</rs> quicquid
                        voluerit, sine omni contradictionem predicte Rose suorumque eredum; et si
                        exinde agere aut causare presumpserit ut componat ipsa res <rs
                            key="#Penalty">in duplo</rs>. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Ambrosius"
                                >Ambrosius</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominicus</name></persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Bonacausa"
                                >Bonacausa</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Albitius/diaconus">Albizo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> seu et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines #Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Angnel/clericus">Iohannes</name>
                            <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> qui Angnel</persName> vocatur et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines" ref="#people/2164"
                            >Albizo dal Casale</persName> interfuerunt. Factum est hoc anno ab
                        incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi milesimo sexagesimo VIIIvo,
                        indictione sexta. </ab>
